  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbe\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 : \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 : \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Unprecedented flood of people in Sri Lanka Invasion towards Colombo: Stalled Colombo: Tear gas used",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "People from many parts of the country are flocking towards the capital Colombo like never before in history.",
        "Colombo, the capital city, has come to a standstill as a major protest is taking place today with the support of many parties in Galle to depose President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "COLOMBO - Today marks the completion of 3 months since the self-insurgency started by young people in the Galle face-off protest demanding the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his government. A demonstration is underway.",
        "Today's demonstration has been organized by empty-faced demonstrators without the involvement of any political party.",
        "Kota - Today's demonstration is being carried out under the theme that we will make the Ranil government resign.",
        "Following the anti-government protest, security has been strengthened by the army and police in several areas of the Colombo Fort."
      ],
